    "subject": "Simplify TimelineMetricCacheTest by using a HashMap",
    "body": "This commit simplifies the TimelineMetricCacheTest by using a HashMap instead of a HashMap<String, TimelineMetric>. This change makes the code more flexible and easier to maintain. The test functionality remains the same, but the code is now more generic and can be used to test any type of object in the map, not just TimelineMetric objects."
